graph TB
    subgraph "Coding Environment (Cursor / Windsurf / Claude Code)"
        Agent[**AI Coding Agent**<br/>OpenAI GPT-4o / Claude 3.5]
        MCP_Client[**MCP Client**<br/>Context Orchestrator]
    end

    subgraph "MCP Server Layer"
        PG_MCP[**Postgres MCP Server**<br/>Exposes Table Schemas]
        FS_MCP[**Filesystem MCP Server**<br/>Exposes Python/TS Code]
    end

    subgraph "Application Backend (FastAPI)"
        API[**FastAPI App**<br/>app/main.py]
        Sync[**Sync Worker**<br/>pg_to_duck_sync]
        Prompt_Eng[**Prompt Orchestrator**<br/>Natural Lang -> Logic]
    end

    subgraph "Data Layer"
        PG[(**PostgreSQL**<br/>Primary / System of Record)]
        DDB[(**DuckDB**<br/>Analytical Engine / Pricing Math)]
    end

    subgraph "Frontend"
        React[**React 18.3**<br/>Vite / AG Grid / Blockly]
    end

    %% Connections
    React -->|Natural Language Requirement| API
    API -->|Schema Retrieval| PG_MCP
    Agent <-->|Queries Metadata| MCP_Client
    MCP_Client <--> PG_MCP
    MCP_Client <--> FS_MCP
    
    PG_MCP <-->|Reads Schema| PG
    FS_MCP <-->|Reads Models/Logic| API
    
    API <-->|Transaction Data| PG
    Sync ---|ETL Pipe| PG
    Sync ---|ETL Pipe| DDB
    API <-->|Heavy Pricing Calcs| DDB
    
